any worse than a number of products I\'ve had the misfortune to actually spend money on. But they\'re distributing Linux (stock Ubuntu with some additional packages and a modified kernel) without any source or an offer to provide source. I emailed them last week and got the following reply:<cite><br /><br />Dear Sir,                                                                                                                                                                                            <br />                                                                                                                                                                                                        <br />we are still actively making changes to the joojoo software. We will make                                                                                                                            <br />the source release available once we feel we are ready to do so and also                                                                                                                             <br />having the resources to get this sorted out and organized for publication.                                                                                                                           <br />We seek your kind understanding on our position and appreciate your                                                                                                                                  <br />patience on this. Thank you.                                                                                                                                                                         <br />                                                                                                                                                                                                     <br />Best Regards                                                    