<p>See the examples and README files in <em>/usr/share/doc/google-sitemapgen/</em> for an introduction into configuring google-sitemapgen.</p>

<p>So far the generated sitemaps works very well, especially for search engines which are not able to use the rss feeds like Google does.</p>
